pull_request.title: adds hybrid KEMs to algorithms reporting list
pull_request.body:
Fixes #408 . This should also be a "quick fix" for https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/issues/83 -- however at the cost of running irrelevant tests in `speed`. 

Thus the suggestion is to not merge this but do an alternative, script-level fix as discussed in https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/issues/83#issuecomment-1326603244. This branch may still be used as a stop-gap if no-one has time to resolve https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/profiling/issues/83 differently but should be deleted if that issue has been resolved for good.
